<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٥٣- غالِب بْن عُبَيد اللهِ، العُقَيلِيُّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِعَ منه يَعلَى بْن عُبَيد، ومُحَمد بْن يُوسُف.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُنكَرُ الحديثِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أُراه الجَزَرِيُّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>يُعَدُّ فِي البَصريين.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>